OL,3,CEx-BBC producer guilty of possessing
OL,4,Cindecent images of children avoids jail
OL,6,FA former BBC producer who was found
OL,7,Fguilty of downloading child abuse
OL,8,Fimages has avoided jail after being
OL,9,Fgiven an 18-month suspended sentence.
OL,11,F50-year-old Dylan Dawes had more than
OL,12,F6,000 indecent images of children on
OL,13,Fhis devices when they were seized by
OL,14,Fpolice.
OL,16,FHe denied having a sexual interest in
OL,17,Fchildren and claimed someone else may
OL,18,Fhave used the devices, which were
OL,19,Fsometimes left overnight at the BBC's
OL,20,FCardiff HQ.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
