PN,46402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778842975
OL,3,CEx-BBC producer guilty of possessing
OL,4,Cindecent images of children avoids jail
OL,6,FDawes, who started working for the BBC
OL,7,Fin 2000, was found guilty of three
OL,8,Fcounts of possessing an indecent image
OL,9,Fof a child, and three counts of making
OL,10,Fan indecent image of a child, relating
OL,11,Fto more than 6,000 images found on his
OL,12,Fdevices at Cardiff Crown Court in
OL,13,FApril.
OL,15,FAt Newport Crown Court on Thursday,
OL,16,FDawes was sentenced to 18 months
OL,17,Fimprisonment, suspended for two years.
OL,19,FHe was also placed on the sex
OL,20,Foffenders' register for 10 years.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
