PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778842975
OL,3,CEx-BBC producer guilty of possessing
OL,4,Cindecent images of children avoids jail
OL,6,FJudge Egan said: "You have paid and
OL,7,Fyou will continue to pay a heavy price
OL,8,Ffor what you did.
OL,10,F"The public humiliation has been, and
OL,11,Fwill continue to be, significant.
OL,13,F"The ball is now in your court to
OL,14,Fensure that you stay out of trouble `
OL,15,FI'm confident that you will."
OL,17,FJudge Egan said Dawes had sought to
OL,18,Fblame "anyone and everyone" who had
OL,19,Faccess to the former BBC offices in
OL,20,FLlandaff, casting suspicion over many
OL,21,Fof his former colleagues.
OL,26,@nD@ROUrD@AOUuD@AOUwD@]O]zD@GOUzD@[O]
