OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778842975
OL,3,CEx-BBC producer guilty of possessing
OL,4,Cindecent images of children avoids jail
OL,6,FHe added: "The real truth, however,
OL,7,Fwas this ` that none of those many
OL,8,Fhundreds of people were to blame.
OL,10,F"You, and you alone, were to blame."
OL,12,FDawes joined the BBC while living in
OL,13,FLondon in 2000 and started his job at
OL,14,FBBC Wales after moving to Cardiff in
OL,15,F2001, where he worked as a producer on
OL,16,Fradio shows and podcasts.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@AOUrD@dO]
