OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778842975
OL,3,CEx-BBC producer guilty of possessing
OL,4,Cindecent images of children avoids jail
OL,6,FThe court heard he was arrested in
OL,7,F2022 after officers searched his
OL,8,FCardiff home, finding indecent images
OL,9,Fon four devices, including a hard
OL,10,Fdrive, laptop and two iPads.
OL,12,FDawes told the court he had "fairly
OL,13,Fregularly" viewed "adult pornography"
OL,14,Fbut denied having downloaded incident
OL,15,Fimages of children.
OL,17,FThe court heard he had "no idea" how
OL,18,Fthe images were downloaded and denied
OL,19,Fhaving used the search term
OL,20,F"jailbait", suggesting someone else
OL,21,Fmay have accessed the devices.
OL,26,@tD@]OUuD@JO]uD@SOUuD@eO]yD@XOUyD@`O]|D@
OL,26,AAOU|D@JO]
