CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778842975
OL,3,CEx-BBC producer guilty of possessing
OL,4,Cindecent images of children avoids jail
OL,6,FHarry Baker, prosecuting, said the
OL,7,Fimages had been found on four of
OL,8,FDawes' devices and it was unlikely
OL,9,Fthis was an "unhappy coincidence".
OL,11,FDawes, of Canton, Cardiff, was
OL,12,Fsuspended from his job at the BBC
OL,13,Fafter his arrest and is no longer
OL,14,Femployed by the broadcaster.
OL,16,FAndrew Taylor, defending, said Dawes
OL,17,Fdid not "shy away" from the findings
OL,18,Fof the court.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@aO]yD@IOUyD@RO]
