OL,3,CEx-BBC producer guilty of possessing
OL,4,Cindecent images of children avoids jail
OL,6,FHe said: "This is a 50-year-old man
OL,7,Fwho has never been before the court in
OL,8,Fhis life.
OL,10,F"This is a man who has lost everything.
OL,12,F"He is coming to terms with his
OL,13,Foffending and he will try his level
OL,14,Fbest to rehabilitate."
